qemu-rpi (1:11.0.0~rc2+ds-2+rpi1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Custom QEMU build with Raspberry Pi 4B GENET Ethernet support.
  * Based on Debian experimental qemu 1:11.0.0~rc2+ds-2.
  * Added 16 patches from Kambalin v6 series ported to QEMU v11:
    - BCM2838 GENET Ethernet controller (bidirectional DMA networking)
    - BCM2838 PCIe Root Complex
    - BCM2838 RNG200 hardware RNG
    - BCM2838 thermal sensor
    - PL011 UART fix for U-Boot handoff
  * Packages renamed to qemu-rpi-* for side-by-side installation
    with standard Debian QEMU packages.
  * Only builds aarch64-softmmu target.

 -- Tim Ansell <mithro@mithis.com>  Mon, 07 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0930
